A **tax-saver FD** is a 5-year fixed deposit that qualifies for deduction up to ₹1.5 lakh under Section 80C (old regime only). It has a mandatory 5-year lock-in period — no premature withdrawal allowed. Interest earned is taxable at slab rates and subject to TDS. It is the safest 80C option but has lower returns than ELSS and PPF.
